\f1\b0\fs28 \cf0 \
Johnson Controls is investing in OpenBlue, a smart building platform that turns raw operational data into actionable intelligence. Before any dashboard or AI tool can be useful, someone has to understand the data \'97 its structure, its quality problems, and what it can and cannot tell you.\
\
In this assignment you will explore real IoT sensor data from a chilled water plant by hand \'97 opening the files, looking at the rows and columns, and discovering what's messy about it. Then you will hand the same data to AI tools and see what AI gets right, gets wrong, and misses entirely. The goal is not to become a data scientist \'97 it is to become the kind of manager who understands both the data and the AI tools used to interpret it.\
\
